[size=3]This is my first attempt to a Redguard Character and i am quite happy with her.[/size]
I was so busy with her sculpt that i literally used Vanilla eyes lol

[size=3]HOW TO INSTALL PRESETS:[/size]
[size=3]
I HIGHLY ADVICE YOU TO MANUALLY INSTALL
Where does the JSLOT file go?:
Go to where you installed your skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets <-- Drop it there

Where does the .NIF and .DDS File go?:
Go to where you installed your skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen <--- Drop it there
